on that today because he mentioned something in the course of our recording=
 that I think is worth calling out as an addendum to yesterday=E2=80=99s Up=
date ( https://stratechery.com/2023/eu-fines-meta-big-tech-exposure-the-deg=
radation-of-scalability/?access_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF=
